<c.bg_transparent>And you,</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:20:02.401 --> 00:20:05.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, um...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't mind my asking that is,</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:59.20 --> 00:20:00.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You... You are...?</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:20:07.399 --> 00:20:10.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Mr. Pabst's new secretary,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Darlene Kursky.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:20:10.678 --> 00:20:11.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which one of youse wrote this?</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:20:12.558 --> 00:20:13.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:20:13.757 --> 00:20:15.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You? Surprised?</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:20:15.636 --> 00:20:19.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... It's the best thing I've read</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Since </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>the puppet masters.</i></c.bg_transparent>

316
00:20:19.355 --> 00:20:20.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I read a lot of science fiction.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:20:21.035 --> 00:20:23.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bless you, my child.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The world needs more people like you.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:20:24.271 --> 00:20:28.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This story is really...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's... It's... Um... Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:20:28.393 --> 00:20:29.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How should I put it?</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:20:30.032 --> 00:20:31.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's... It's very...</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:32.071 --> 00:20:34.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Impressive?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:20:34.631 --> 00:20:36.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a damn fine piece</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of writing is what it is.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:37.470 --> 00:20:40.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> deep space nine</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> is a very</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>intriguing title.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:20:40.629 --> 00:20:41.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very admirable.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:20:41.869 --> 00:20:43.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The master of understatement.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:20:43.429 --> 00:20:46.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What he really means is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He wishes he had half your talent.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:20:46.828 --> 00:20:48.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KAY: You know what, Benny?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:20:48.267 --> 00:20:50.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like this major. She's a tough cookie.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:20:51.186 --> 00:20:54.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Science fiction needs more strong women.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm always saying that, aren't I?</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:20:55.178 --> 00:20:56.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ad nauseam, dear.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:56.384 --> 00:20:59.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These Cardassians...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I like the way you described them,</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:59.663 --> 00:21:00.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Especially the neck ridges.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:21:01.223 --> 00:21:04.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to do some sketches,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make a nice cover.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:21:04.782 --> 00:21:05.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't waste your time.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:21:06.142 --> 00:21:08.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You, get back to work. You, too, Roy.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:21:08.661 --> 00:21:10.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Douglas, you're not going to tell us</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:21:10.740 --> 00:21:12.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You don't like this story.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, I like it.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:21:12.740 --> 00:21:15.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very good.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>But you know I can't print it.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:21:15.779 --> 00:21:17.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Why not?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, come on, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:21:18.098 --> 00:21:19.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your hero's a Negro Captain,</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:21:20.097 --> 00:21:22.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The head of a space station,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Christ's sake.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:21:22.697 --> 00:21:23.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with that?</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:21:24.137 --> 00:21:26.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>People won't accept it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's not believable.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:21:26.856 --> 00:21:30.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And men from mars are?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-PABST: Stay out of this, Herb.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:21:30.295 --> 00:21:34.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, Benny, I am a magazine editor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I am not a crusader.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:21:34.533 --> 00:21:37.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not here to change the world.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm here to put out a magazine.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:21:37.612 --> 00:21:39.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That means I have to answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the publisher,</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:21:40.841 --> 00:21:42.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The national distributors,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the wholesalers,</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:21:42.491 --> 00:21:45.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and none of them are going to want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>To put this story on the newsstand.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:21:46.024 --> 00:21:47.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For all we know, it could cause</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a race riot.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:21:48.209 --> 00:21:50.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Douglas.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:21:51.048 --> 00:21:55.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the most imbecilic attempt</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>To rationalize personal cowardice</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:21:56.246 --> 00:21:57.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That I've ever heard.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:21:57.646 --> 00:21:59.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh. He's angry now.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:21:59.246 --> 00:22:02.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Huh! Herb's been angry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ever since Josef Stalin died.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:22:02.325 --> 00:22:04.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that supposed to mean?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You know exactly what it means.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:22:05.366 --> 00:22:06.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You calling me a red?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Easy, easy.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:22:06.843 --> 00:22:10.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calm down, dear boy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're writers, not vikings.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:22:11.043 --> 00:22:14.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to stand here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and let some craven fascist call me</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:22:14.481 --> 00:22:16.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HERB: a pinko and get away with it.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:17.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Douglas, um...</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:21.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did you think of, uh... of my story?</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:22:21.878 --> 00:22:25.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I loved it. Albert's got the right idea.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's not interested in Negroes or whites.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:22:25.678 --> 00:22:28.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He writes about robots.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's because he is a robot.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:22:29.517 --> 00:22:30.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No offense, Albert.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:22:31.276 --> 00:22:32.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I...</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:22:32.796 --> 00:22:38.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like robots.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're very... Uh... Uh, efficient.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:22:39.666 --> 00:22:40.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here. Write me a novella</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>based on this picture.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:22:41.656 --> 00:22:43.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll print it in next month's issue.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:22:43.393 --> 00:22:45.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You do a good job,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you might even get the cover.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:22:45.392 --> 00:22:47.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What about my story?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The way I see it,</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:22:47.551 --> 00:22:49.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can either burn it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or stick it in a drawer</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:22:49.310 --> 00:22:51.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the next 50 years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or how ever long it takes</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:22:51.150 --> 00:22:54.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The human race to become color-blind.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want people to read it now.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:22:54.070 --> 00:22:56.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want me to print it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make the Captain white.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:22:56.908 --> 00:22:57.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not what I wrote!</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:22:58.748 --> 00:22:59.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your call.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:23:16.582 --> 00:23:18.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry they didn't buy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your story, baby.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:23:18.781 --> 00:23:19.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really I am.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:23:19.901 --> 00:23:23.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you you were wasting your time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A colored Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:23:24.129 --> 00:23:26.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they'll ever let us in space</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:23:26.380 --> 00:23:28.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is if they need someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to shine their shoes.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:23:28.699 --> 00:23:29.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ain't that right, Cassie?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:23:30.178 --> 00:23:31.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know, and to be honest.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:23:31.778 --> 00:23:34.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't much care what happens</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a hundred years from now.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:23:35.097 --> 00:23:36.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's today that matters.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:23:36.297 --> 00:23:37.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I've got news for you.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:23:37.856 --> 00:23:40.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Today or 100 years from now,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It don't make a bit of difference.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:23:41.135 --> 00:23:44.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As far as they're concerned,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll always be niggers.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:23:45.461 --> 00:23:47.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Things are going to change. They have to.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:23:47.694 --> 00:23:49.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you keep telling yourself that.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:23:49.812 --> 00:23:51.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe this is all happening for a reason.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:23:52.440 --> 00:23:53.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean maybe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's God's way of telling me</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:23:53.891 --> 00:23:56.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should quit writing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and go into the restaurant business?</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:23:56.890 --> 00:23:58.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, it's possible.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:24:00.649 --> 00:24:04.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Baby, I know we can make this work for us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We could be happy.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:24:04.768 --> 00:24:07.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, you don't have to give up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Writing altogether.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:24:07.207 --> 00:24:09.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you could write something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Amsterdam news</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:24:10.389 --> 00:24:12.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or... Some other Negro newspaper.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:24:12.685 --> 00:24:16.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not a reporter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a writer. I write fiction,</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:24:16.565 --> 00:24:19.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the Amsterdam news</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is not going to publish stories</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:24:19.324 --> 00:24:22.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>about a space station 400 years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into the future.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:24:24.242 --> 00:24:25.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hear the game last night?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:24:25.802 --> 00:24:27.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:24:29.730 --> 00:24:31.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't mean to frighten you.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:24:31.680 --> 00:24:34.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't look so good.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You sick or something?</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:24:34.879 --> 00:24:37.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, no, I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You want to lie down in the back?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:24:37.118 --> 00:24:38.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I... I just need some air.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:24:38.678 --> 00:24:40.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are we still on for tonight?</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:24:40.557 --> 00:24:42.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll pick you up about 10:00.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:24:44.286 --> 00:24:44.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Door shuts )</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:24:45.276 --> 00:24:47.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, what are you doing till 10:00?</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:24:47.915 --> 00:24:50.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whatever it is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I won't be doing it with you.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:24:59.352 --> 00:25:00.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PREACHER: Hello, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:25:02.751 --> 00:25:03.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you again.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:25:04.350 --> 00:25:06.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand what you want from me.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:25:06.589 --> 00:25:08.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To follow the path of the prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:25:09.509 --> 00:25:11.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Walk with the prophets, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:25:12.587 --> 00:25:14.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Show us the way.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:25:14.227 --> 00:25:15.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>W--what way?</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:25:15.707 --> 00:25:19.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't know what you're talking about.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Write the words, brother Benny...</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:25:19.666 --> 00:25:22.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>PREACHER: The words that will lead</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>us out of the darkness</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:25:22.505 --> 00:25:27.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Onto the path of righteousness!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Write the words, brother Benny!</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:25:27.543 --> 00:25:28.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Write the words!</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:25:54.295 --> 00:25:58.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Playing slow jazz )</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:26:09.691 --> 00:26:10.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, baby.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:26:11.029 --> 00:26:12.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, hey, hey.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:26:12.730 --> 00:26:14.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You forgot all about our date.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:26:14.769 --> 00:26:18.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ohh... Our date. I'm sorry. I was working.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:26:20.804 --> 00:26:22.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ben Sisko?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Isn't that your colored Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:26:22.527 --> 00:26:23.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:26:24.127 --> 00:26:26.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you writing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another one of those stories?</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:26:26.406 --> 00:26:29.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You couldn't sell the last one.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what makes you think this one</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:26:29.325 --> 00:26:30.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be any different?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:26:30.884 --> 00:26:33.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It probably won't be,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:26:34.283 --> 00:26:37.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's what I've got to do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Right now, what you've got to do is eat.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:26:38.602 --> 00:26:40.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not hungry. ( Yawning )</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:26:41.281 --> 00:26:42.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What time is it anyway?</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:26:45.120 --> 00:26:48.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's after midnight.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I should be getting home to bed.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:26:49.712 --> 00:26:52.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But before I go, what do you say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we take a spin on the dance floor?</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:26:53.118 --> 00:26:54.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Okay.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:27:04.634 --> 00:27:07.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm. Feels good, doesn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:27:08.233 --> 00:27:10.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could stay like this forever.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:27:10.873 --> 00:27:12.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm, me, too. It's times like these</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:27:12.831 --> 00:27:15.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That I wish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'd never heard of the Dominion.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:27:15.071 --> 00:27:16.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Dominion?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:27:16.351 --> 00:27:17.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:27:18.629 --> 00:27:20.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said something about the Dominion.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:27:22.069 --> 00:27:23.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it, Ben?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:27:23.708 --> 00:27:25.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:27:25.628 --> 00:27:27.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:27:27.107 --> 00:27:28.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I'm losing my mind.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:27:31.866 --> 00:27:36.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm starting to see things from my story.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:27:36.385 --> 00:27:39.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's as if I'm becoming</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this Captain Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:27:40.024 --> 00:27:42.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Okay, baby,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you just need to get some rest.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:27:42.222 --> 00:27:45.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right. It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:27:45.023 --> 00:27:46.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm with you. I'm with you, baby.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:27:47.537 --> 00:27:49.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just take it easy. Shh.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:27:54.620 --> 00:27:56.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you lost your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:27:57.138 --> 00:27:59.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been asking myself the same question.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:27:59.297 --> 00:28:01.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I give you a novella to write,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I even offer you a shot at the cover.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:28:01.817 --> 00:28:03.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three weeks later instead of a novella,</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:28:03.377 --> 00:28:04.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You come back with six stories,</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:28:05.888 --> 00:28:07.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Six </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>sequels </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>to a story</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I refused to publish</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:28:07.535 --> 00:28:11.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the first place. So I guess the answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>To the question we've both been asking</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:28:11.894 --> 00:28:16.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is, yeah, you are certifiable.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think you should print your own stories</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:28:16.493 --> 00:28:20.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Through a private publishing house.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A nice, elegant volume 50 to 100 copies.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:28:20.731 --> 00:28:22.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a great idea.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:28:22.291 --> 00:28:24.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, might as well write it in chalk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the sidewalk.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:28:24.170 --> 00:28:26.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>More people would read it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:28:26.827 --> 00:28:31.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got an idea.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Why not make them, you know, a, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:28:31.806 --> 00:28:33.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A d--dream?</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:28:36.126 --> 00:28:37.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:28:37.087 --> 00:28:39.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just make the ending</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:28:39.086 --> 00:28:42.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of your first story</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>deep space nine </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>a...</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:28:43.245 --> 00:28:44.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dream.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:28:45.644 --> 00:28:47.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would that make a difference?</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:28:47.443 --> 00:28:48.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:28:50.322 --> 00:28:52.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On what?</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:28:52.745 --> 00:28:53.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On who's doing the dreaming.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:28:53.601 --> 00:28:57.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, obviously someone, uh...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Someone without a lot of hope.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:28:57.600 --> 00:29:01.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A--a shoeshine boy, a convict...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Someone dreaming of a better future.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:29:02.319 --> 00:29:03.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:29:04.311 --> 00:29:04.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Negro.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:29:05.158 --> 00:29:09.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, well, I suppose he'd have to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if he was dreaming about a Negro Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:29:09.557 --> 00:29:11.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HERB: Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:29:11.196 --> 00:29:14.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Making it a dream guts the story.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Shut up, Herb!</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:29:15.195 --> 00:29:16.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it makes it more poignant.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:29:16.675 --> 00:29:19.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about the other Sisko stories?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You can't make them all a dream.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:29:19.554 --> 00:29:22.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let him get this published,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then worry about the others.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:29:23.273 --> 00:29:24.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you think, Benny?</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:29:26.672 --> 00:29:27.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think...</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:29:29.271 --> 00:29:31.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's better than chalk on the sidewalk.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:29:34.621 --> 00:29:34.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I play?</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:29:35.709 --> 00:29:38.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, Jimmy, I got great news.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We are headed for the stars.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:29:38.588 --> 00:29:40.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, sure, whatever.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:29:40.188 --> 00:29:41.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, come on.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll buy you lunch.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:29:41.428 --> 00:29:42.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll tell you all about it.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:29:42.347 --> 00:29:44.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Later. I got some business</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to take care of.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:29:44.226 --> 00:29:45.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What kind of business?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:29:45.466 --> 00:29:47.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Big time. That's all I'm saying.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:29:47.225 --> 00:29:48.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, hold it. Hold it.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:29:48.785 --> 00:29:49.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:29:50.570 --> 00:29:50.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry about it.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:29:51.570 --> 00:29:52.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's cool, I got it under control.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Huh?</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:29:53.503 --> 00:29:54.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see you around.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:29:57.542 --> 00:29:59.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bottom of the seventh, I'm up again.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:29:59.502 --> 00:30:02.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>O-2 fast ball... bam!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Into the left field bleachers.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:30:03.260 --> 00:30:05.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Had to be 400 feet.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:30:05.260 --> 00:30:08.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know all about it, Willie.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I read the newspaper.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:30:08.259 --> 00:30:09.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, but you got to admit...</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:30:10.179 --> 00:30:11.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They don't tell it like I tell it.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:30:13.058 --> 00:30:14.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BENNY: Hey, Cassie!</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:30:17.416 --> 00:30:18.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Giggles )</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:30:18.297 --> 00:30:20.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WILLIE: Hey, man, did you hear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the game last night?</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:30:20.176 --> 00:30:21.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
