624
00:36:40.103 --> 00:36:41.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's his decision.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:36:42.941 --> 00:36:45.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you can't fire me.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:36:46.044 --> 00:36:49.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I quit. To hell with you...</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:50.499 --> 00:36:52.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And to hell with Stone.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:52.779 --> 00:36:54.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try to stay calm, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:36:54.139 --> 00:36:58.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! I'm tired of being calm.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Calm never got me a damn thing.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:36:58.257 --> 00:36:59.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm warning you, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:36:59.217 --> 00:37:01.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't stop this,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to call the police.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:37:01.697 --> 00:37:03.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You go ahead! Call them!</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:04.055 --> 00:37:07.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Call anybody you want.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They can't do anything to me.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:07.335 --> 00:37:09.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not anymore... And nor can any of you!</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:15.757 --> 00:37:19.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... Am a human being, damn it.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:20.650 --> 00:37:26.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can deny me all you want...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>But you cannot deny Ben Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:26.089 --> 00:37:26.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He exists.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:37:27.528 --> 00:37:32.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That future, that space station,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all those people, they exist in here.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:37:33.647 --> 00:37:39.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In my mind. I created it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And every one of you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:39.365 --> 00:37:40.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You read it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:41.165 --> 00:37:44.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's here. You get what I'm telling you?</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:45.272 --> 00:37:49.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can pulp a story,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you cannot destroy an idea.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:37:49.282 --> 00:37:51.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you understand?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That's ancient knowledge.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:37:51.801 --> 00:37:54.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You cannot destroy an idea.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:37:56.480 --> 00:38:00.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That future I created it, and it's real!</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:38:00.958 --> 00:38:03.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you understand?</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:38:03.518 --> 00:38:08.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is real! I created it, and it's real!</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:09.037 --> 00:38:12.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's real. Oh, god!</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:13.395 --> 00:38:15.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Weeping )</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:26.431 --> 00:38:27.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PARAMEDIC: Easy...</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:40.547 --> 00:38:41.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One... two... three.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:39:02.340 --> 00:39:04.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rest easy, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:39:04.339 --> 00:39:07.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have walked in the path</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:39:07.299 --> 00:39:09.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no greater glory.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:39:10.015 --> 00:39:11.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, please.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:39:12.137 --> 00:39:13.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who am I?</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:39:14.004 --> 00:39:15.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you know?</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:39:15.616 --> 00:39:16.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:39:17.775 --> 00:39:20.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the dreamer...</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:39:21.054 --> 00:39:23.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the dream.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:39:38.290 --> 00:39:39.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KASIDY: Ben.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:39:41.169 --> 00:39:42.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ben?</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:52.085 --> 00:39:54.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How long was I out?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Only for a few minutes.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:39:55.364 --> 00:39:57.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seemed like forever to me.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:39:58.243 --> 00:39:59.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's odd.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:40:00.264 --> 00:40:02.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somehow your neural patterns</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have returned to normal.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:40:02.522 --> 00:40:05.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's good, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, it's very good.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:40:05.162 --> 00:40:07.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just don't understand how it happened.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:40:14.678 --> 00:40:16.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling, son?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:40:16.957 --> 00:40:18.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm okay.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:40:19.437 --> 00:40:21.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm done packing.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:40:21.836 --> 00:40:24.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Transport leaves at 8:00 in the morning.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:40:25.115 --> 00:40:27.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish you could stay longer.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:40:27.834 --> 00:40:29.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to get back to the restaurant.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:40:30.553 --> 00:40:33.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My customers have never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gone this long without me.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:40:35.112 --> 00:40:38.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The question is what are you going to do?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:40:40.671 --> 00:40:45.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only thing I can do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Stay here and finish the job I started,</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:40:46.589 --> 00:40:47.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if I fail...</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:40:48.228 --> 00:40:53.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"I have fought the good fight...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have finished the course...</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:40:54.100 --> 00:40:55.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have kept the faith."</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:40:57.346 --> 00:40:58.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never known you to quote</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the bible.</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:40:59.745 --> 00:41:02.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm full of surprises, aren't I?</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:41:04.104 --> 00:41:05.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And so are you.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:41:06.663 --> 00:41:10.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sounds like that dream</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you had... Helped you sort things out.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:41:11.342 --> 00:41:12.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose it did...</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:41:13.981 --> 00:41:16.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have begun to wonder.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:17.179 --> 00:41:18.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it wasn't a dream?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:41:19.979 --> 00:41:23.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if this life we're leading,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all of this...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:41:24.818 --> 00:41:31.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and me, everything...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What if all of this is the illusion?</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:41:32.455 --> 00:41:34.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a scary thought.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:41:35.334 --> 00:41:36.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know. I know.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:41:37.414 --> 00:41:39.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But maybe, just maybe...</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:41:39.813 --> 00:41:41.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny isn't the dream.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:41:42.614 --> 00:41:42.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:41:44.390 --> 00:41:48.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we're nothing more than figments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his imagination.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:41:50.996 --> 00:41:51.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For all we know...</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:41:53.347 --> 00:41:54.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this very moment,</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:41:55.227 --> 00:41:59.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somewhere far beyond</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all those distant stars...</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:42:00.905 --> 00:42:02.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny Russell...</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:42:03.104 --> 00:42:04.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is dreaming of us.</c.bg_transparent>

